OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780920676
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to murder of Sarah
OL,4,CMontgomery
OL,6,FA 29-year old man has been handed a
OL,7,Flife sentence after he admitted
OL,8,Fmurdering his pregnant partner Sarah
OL,9,FMontgomery in her Donaghadee home.
OL,11,FZak Hughes also admitted a charge of
OL,12,Fcausing the destruction of her unborn
OL,13,Fchild.
OL,15,FThe 27-year old mother-of-two was
OL,16,Fkilled in her Elmfield Walk home on
OL,17,FJune 27, 2025. As a result of the
OL,18,Ffatal attack, her unborn son did not
OL,19,Fsurvive.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
