PN,44505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780920676
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to murder of Sarah
OL,4,CMontgomery
OL,6,FCrown barrister Geraldine McCullough
OL,7,FKC then told Madam Justice McBride she
OL,8,Fanticipated there will be Victim
OL,9,FImpact Statements from Ms Montgomery's
OL,10,Ffamily.
OL,12,FRegarding the defence, Mr Jones said
OL,13,Fhe would be seeking a Pre Sentence
OL,14,FReport on Hughes.
OL,16,FMadam Justice McBride then set the
OL,17,Fdate for the Tariff hearing as Friday
OL,18,FSeptember 11, 2026.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
